doctype html
html
  head(lang="en")
    meta(http-equiv="content-type", content="text/html; charset=UTF-8")
    meta(name="description", content="A portfolio that stacks up")
    meta(name="keywords", content="")
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, user-scalable=no')
    title Portfolio - view our work
    style.
      body { display: none; }
    link(rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico")
  body
    .overflowWrap(id="home")
      include ./components/nav
      .ks-portfolio
        h1 Our Portfolio
        .image-slider
          .slider-arrow(id="slider-left")
            img(src="assets/images/arrow-left.svg")
          .images
            img.slider-img(src="assets/images/portfolio/bablot-min.png")
            img.slider-img(src="assets/images/portfolio/beamer-min.png")
            img.slider-img(src="assets/images/portfolio/botany-min.png")
          .slider-arrow(id="slider-right")
            img(src="assets/images/arrow-right.svg")
        .blurbs
          .blurb.show(id="blurb-0")
            h2 Bablot
            p Bablot is a communications tool for Property Rental managers. It uses Facebook messenger to automate responses, and turn after hour visitors into valuable leads. After designing the web portal, we implemented the app in Angular 2 and Node, then finally deployed with Docker.
            p To top it all off we crafted <i>7 custom AI chat bots</i> from the ground up for a variety of property rental managers.
          .blurb(id="blurb-1")
            h2 Beamer
            p Beamer is an unopinionated CMS for bloggers and creators. It provides a rich interface for creating, storing, and managing content but gives you complete freedom over how you <i>use</i> that content.
            p Beamer provides a full RESTful api for developers to inject their content wherever and whenever they want.
          .blurb(id="blurb-2")
            h2 Botany
            p Botany is changing the way people make chat bots. We designed custom software to let people create intelligent chatbots with no code. Botany features tons of plugins that enhance bots with things like payments, booking appointments, and more!
            p For developers, we built an open API to give anyone the power to integrate chat bots into their existing platform.
      include ./components/footer
      script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.4.min.js', integrity='sha256-BbhdlvQf/xTY9gja0Dq3HiwQF8LaCRTXxZKRutelT44=', crossorigin='anonymous')
      script(src="main.min.js")
      script.
        loadCSS( "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Concert+One");
        var stylesheet = loadCSS( "main.css" );
        onloadCSS( stylesheet, function() {
          setInterval(function() {
            $("body").css("display","block");
            initSlick();
          }, 200);
        });
